All Implemented Interfaces:
Stream
public class H264Stream
extends VideoStream

A class for streaming H.264 from the camera of an android device using RTP. Call MediaStream.setDestinationAddress(java.net.InetAddress), MediaStream.setDestinationPorts(int), VideoStream.setVideoSize(int, int), VideoStream.setVideoFramerate(int) and VideoStream.setVideoEncodingBitrate(int) and you're good to go. You can then call VideoStream.start(). Call VideoStream.stop() to stop the stream.
